<DATELINE>
   PARIS
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
FRENCH pharmaceutical goods distributor and manufacturer Cooperation
Pharmaceutique Francaise and distributor Bergen Brunswick of the US have
dropped their bid for Office Commercial Pharmaceutique (OCP), Paris Bourse
authorities announced, AP-DJ reports from Paris.
