FT  19 JUN 93 / World Commodities Prices: Spices
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
The market was fully steady for both black and white, at origins as well as
in importing countries, reports Man Producten. In the European white market
Muntok, spot, was fetching Dollars 1,950 a tonne, with June/July at Dollars
