Sarawak, China and Brazil. Among the black peppers Sarawak black label was
unquoted on the spot market but June/July was offered at Dollars 1,215 a
tonne. Neither was there a spot quotation for Sarawak yellow label.
June/July was at Dollars 1,265 a tonne. Brazil grade 1, spot, was quoted at
